Class WatchDog

  • java.lang.Object
    • function.WatchDog

  • public class WatchDog
extends java.lang.Object
    Class represent action manager in which actions can be registered and every hour WatchDog checks for actions to be made a performs according actions
    Author:
    Martin Hamet
